title: MusicCast WX-010 Wireless Speaker Overview
description:
Amazingly Big Sound, Surprisingly Small Size

With a stylish, space-saving design that fits anywhere in your home, this MusicCast speaker lets you stream music wirelessly using your existing Wi-Fi network. Use it as a standalone streaming music speaker or add other MusicCast products over time and control it all with a simple app. Two units can be used in stereo mode for a more expansive and lifelike listening experience.

Learn More: http://4wrd.it/WX-010
